Package org.apache.hcatalog.hbase.snapshot.lock

Interface Summary
LockListener This class has two methods which are call back methods when a lock is acquired and when the lock is released.
ZooKeeperOperation A callback object which can be used for implementing retry-able operations in the ProtocolSupport class This class has been used as-is from the zookeeper 3.4.0 with change in the package name .
 

Class Summary
WriteLock A protocol to implement an exclusive write lock or to elect a leader.
ZNodeName Represents an ephemeral znode name which has an ordered sequence number and can be sorted in order This class has been used as-is from the zookeeper 3.4.0 recipes with a change in package name.
